countries across the world to Lustica Bay [ https://substack.com/redirect/f=
c95e0f2-1dc0-4559-a5ca-b60c0054c0e7?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNua=
MZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]=E2=80=94where they lived, shared meals, co-wo=
rked, and held mini-conferences on network states, longevity science, synth=
etic biology, and more. Zuzalu is one example of a broader phenomenon=E2=80=
=94dozens of digitally crowd-sourced cities and network states are starting=
