tps://substack.com/redirect/aab8e71b-3d2f-493a-acb5-30bae32c4030?j=3DeyJ1Ij=
oiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]. Packy and Jill =
Gunter [ https://substack.com/redirect/070c2b75-642f-4ecb-99b9-458024cdf71f=
?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] teame=
d up to write a great piece on zero-knowledge proofs [ https://substack.com=
/redirect/5d0486b3-9435-4165-ad73-6e67ea1ed7af?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5=
T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] if you want to go deeper here, but=
