olor: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><sp=
an>Today&#8217;s post is a guest post from Not Boring&#8217;s very own Biot=
ech Partner, </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/20101fac-0a90-=
4a08-81f9-ba1cd011b55e?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqO=
