/span><em>beautiful</em><span>.</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>The fundamental=
 insight of synthetic biology is that our fastest path to viable nanotechno=
logy is to learn how to program biology</strong><span>. According to Drew E=
